::KitKat::

She looked around.  She turned to Rowdy, "What do you make of all 
this? They couldn't have vanished into thin air.  They didn't leave 
the cave because their scent is too strong right here.  They aren't 
dead or thier bodies would either be on the floor or floating in the 
pool. So where could they have gone? Swimming and found a cave with 
air somewhere down there do you think?"
